WEBVTT

00:06:01.167 --> 00:06:06.696
we could restore control and dignity
to those individuals

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:10.075
by giving them a home,
but not just any home:

00:06:11.165 --> 00:06:12.315
their home,

00:06:12.823 --> 00:06:14.623
and a home of their design.

00:06:15.756 --> 00:06:19.855
We're currently adapting our game
so that when a player builds a home,

00:06:19.879 --> 00:06:22.852
they're contributing to a home
for someone in need.

00:06:23.791 --> 00:06:26.069
